Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,CHORUS. Public Affairs trainees rehearse five audiences before they\Npress send.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: AI-Enabled Public Affairs Training and Audience\NSimulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen synthetic personas across domestic media, host-nation, and\Nadversary IO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a scenario. A drone strike near a host-nation village. The clock\Nis running.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A trainee drafts the release. CHORUS runs it past five personas in\Nparallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Each persona returns structured JSON: trust delta, narrative risk,\Npredicted action.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Five color-coded persona cards. Aggregate trust delta and\Ncounter-message risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed hero model writes a one-page Message Effectiveness\NBrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs inside the wire. No data\Nmovement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Train PA officers in hours, not months.
